              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-brand-teal mr-3">•</span>
                <span><a href="https://github.com/Project-MONAI/tutorials" class="link-hover">Tutorial Repository</a></span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
